===Verb===
'''to decompose''' ([[decomposes]], [[decomposed]], [[decomposing]])
#{{transitive}} to [[separate]] or [[break down]] something into its [[components]]; to [[disintegrate]] or [[fragment]]
#{{intransitive}} to [[rot]], [[decay]] or [[putrefy]]

